OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mixture of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fshowers for most, although some areas
OL,7,Fwill remain dry. Showers most frequent
OL,8,Fin the north and west, and these
OL,9,Fbecoming slow moving across central
OL,10,Fand eastern Scotland. Feeling rather
OL,11,Fcool with temperatures below normal.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers becoming less
OL,14,Ffrequent into the evening but likely
OL,15,Fto persist particularly in the west.
OL,16,FSkies remaining cloudy and feeling
OL,17,Fchilly, especially in rural areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
