OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy with showers or
OL,6,Flonger spells of rain in places. A
OL,7,Fcontinued risk of hail and thunder in
OL,8,Fcentral and eastern areas. Some sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Breezy and feeling cool.
